------------------------------------------------------------------------

@node PROBS "Known problems"
KNOWN PROBLEMS
--------------

MEMORY: On 1 meg machines you might find that, after you've entered quite a
few payslips, the load/save routines start crashing due to lack of memory.
No easy solution to this I'm afraid, except for buying more ram...

PATCHES: I've also found that UltraPayAdvice can be a little bit unstable
when some patches/programs are running - it looks as if the program does
*not* like any of the following...

    Prop3D (patch to add a 3D look to GT proportional gadgets & sliders)

If you're having problems (or experiencing unexplained crashes) and have
got any of the above programs installed, then have a go at removing them
and seeing if the problem still occurs.
@endnode

